# Plan: All Products Block

## Context

Implementing the "All products" block per the spec in `_docs/specs/01 products block`. This is a new reusable theme block that displays all products from a merchant-selected collection in a client-side sortable CSS grid. Designed for small catalogs (~10 products), with no pagination needed.

## Files to Create

- `blocks/all-products.liquid` — the new block

## Files to Modify

- `locales/en.default.json` — add sort button labels and empty state messages
- `locales/en.default.schema.json` — add block name, setting labels, and sort option strings

