## Schema Settings

### Headers and settings (in order)

| Section header | Setting ID | Type | Default |
|---|---|---|---|
| `t:content.content` | `collection` | collection | — |
| `t:content.sorting` | `default_sort` | select | `"price-asc"` |
| | `show_sort_price_asc` | checkbox | `true` |
| | `show_sort_price_desc` | checkbox | `true` |
| | `show_sort_name_asc` | checkbox | `true` |
| | `show_sort_name_desc` | checkbox | `true` |
| `t:content.grid` | `columns` | range 1–8 | `4` |
| | `mobile_columns` | select `"1"\|"2"` | `"2"` |
| | `columns_gap` | range 0–100px | `8` |
| | `rows_gap` | range 0–100px | `8` |
| `t:content.section_layout` | `section_width` | select | `"page-width"` |
| | `color_scheme` | color_scheme | `"scheme-1"` |
| `t:content.padding` | `padding-block-start` | range 0–100px | `48` |
| | `padding-block-end` | range 0–100px | `48` |

Labels for `columns_gap` and `rows_gap` use existing keys `t:settings.horizontal_gap` / `t:settings.vertical_gap`.

Section width options: `t:options.page` / `t:options.full`.

